From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: GE-Proton <git@localhost>
Date: Tue, 7 Jul 2026 00:00:03 -0600
Subject: [PATCH] mmdevapi: Warn about overlong endpoint property names.

Spider-Man Remastered's managed audio endpoint enumeration can crash with an
InvalidCastException after querying render endpoints when an endpoint friendly
name exceeds the practical length tolerated by some apps/libs.

Keep endpoint enumeration intact and log this condition unconditionally, but do
not mutate the returned endpoint property string. Some games also compare these
properties against the underlying endpoint metadata, and truncating the returned
string can create a new mismatch.
---
 dlls/mmdevapi/devenum.c | 11 +++++------
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+), 6 deletions(-)

diff --git a/dlls/mmdevapi/devenum.c b/dlls/mmdevapi/devenum.c
index 4d5bff2b653..a8479226b69 100644
--- a/dlls/mmdevapi/devenum.c
+++ b/dlls/mmdevapi/devenum.c
@@ -2373,13 +2373,12 @@ static HRESULT WINAPI MMDevPropStore_GetValue(IPropertyStore *iface, REFPROPERTY
     if (FAILED(hres))
         return hres;
 
-    if (WARN_ON(mmdevapi))
+    if ((IsEqualPropertyKey(*key, DEVPKEY_Device_FriendlyName) ||
+         IsEqualPropertyKey(*key, DEVPKEY_DeviceInterface_FriendlyName) ||
+         IsEqualPropertyKey(*key, DEVPKEY_Device_DeviceDesc)) &&
+        pv->vt == VT_LPWSTR && wcslen(pv->pwszVal) > 62)
     {
-        if ((IsEqualPropertyKey(*key, DEVPKEY_Device_FriendlyName) ||
-             IsEqualPropertyKey(*key, DEVPKEY_DeviceInterface_FriendlyName) ||
-             IsEqualPropertyKey(*key, DEVPKEY_Device_DeviceDesc)) &&
-            pv->vt == VT_LPWSTR && wcslen(pv->pwszVal) > 62)
-            WARN("Returned name exceeds length limit of some broken apps/libs, might crash: %s\n", debugstr_w(pv->pwszVal));
+        WARN("Returned name exceeds length limit of some broken apps/libs, might crash: %s\n", debugstr_w(pv->pwszVal));
     }
     return hres;
 }
